headline: Jack Henry Study Uncovers Gaps in Consumer Financial Confidence and Digital Experience
summary: With the holiday season in full swing – a time when financial stress often peaks – Jack Henry™ (Nasdaq: JKHY) today released its 2025 Financial Sentiment Study: Consumer Report. The survey of 2,435 individuals across five distinct consumer segments reveals how consumers feel about their financial health and where financial institutions can step in to build trust and deliver meaningful guidance.
